@base_url = http://localhost:3000/api/categories

### Get All Categories
GET {{base_url}}?pageNo=0&pageSize=10

### Get Category by ID
GET {{base_url}}/1

### Create a New Category
POST {{base_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics"
}

### Update Category
PUT {{base_url}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Electronics"
}

### Delete Category
DELETE {{base_url}}/1
